{"tid":2339893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大坑(大波)醉洋漢街頭搶狗抱回寓所 疑打爛燈罩暴行蹤","createTime":"2020-12-25T04:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T04:30:02.000Z","uid":131917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c05063e5ee89e72b1442bb919c9ac7d338f6dcc7","tid":2339893,"uid":131917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%91%E9%86%89%E6%B4%8B%E6%BC%A2%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%E6%90%B6%E7%8B%97%E6%8A%B1%E5%9B%9E%E5%AF%93%E6%89%80-%E7%96%91%E6%89%93%E7%88%9B%E7%87%88%E7%BD%A9%E6%9A%B4%E8%A1%8C%E8%B9%A4-032500201.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259D%2591%25E9%2586%2589%25E6%25B4%258B%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%25A1%2597%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%2590%25B6%25E7%258B%2597%25E6%258A%25B1%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25AF%2593%25E6%2589%2580-%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%2588%259B%25E7%2587%2588%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25B9%25A4-032500201.html&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt60EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=9c4667de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%91%E9%86%89%E6%B4%8B%E6%BC%A2%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%E6%90%B6%E7%8B%97%E6%8A%B1%E5%9B%9E%E5%AF%93%E6%89%80-%E7%96%91%E6%89%93%E7%88%9B%E7%87%88%E7%BD%A9%E6%9A%B4%E8%A1%8C%E8%B9%A4-032500201.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】大坑今日清晨有人偷狗，一名女子帶同一隻法國鬥牛犬，在大坑春暉臺1號對開，一名外籍男子上前逗玩狗狗，其後突然將其抱走拔足狂逃。女子報案，警方在附近成功拘捕該名男子及找回狗狗。<br />\n<br />\n今早約6時許，女子帶同愛犬行至大坑春暉臺1號對開，一名外籍男子上前搭訕及逗玩狗狗，女子不疑有詐，豈料男子竟突然抱走狗狗逃走。<br />\n<br />\n女子報警求助，警員接報到場，在附近的福群道頌月花園外，發現有燈罩被毀，滿地玻璃碎片。警方之後入屋苑搜查，發現涉案男子及狗狗。警方拘捕男子，他身上有酒氣，報稱不適由救護車送院。警方正就案件展開調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tWF885H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWF885H.jpg&h=7a899fef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7588a8de2df67663a5ac772dbe7375cbdc998103","tid":2339893,"uid":362754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T04:30:02.000Z","msg":"好撚大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}